				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-S%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng/B%E1%BA%A1ch-%C4%90%E1%BA%B1ng-giang/poem-7iGqqese4avASlIeUo469g">Bạch Đằng giang - 白藤江</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-S%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng/author-jcnyctA2yI9a8upP-Bt9aw">Nguyễn Sưởng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/B%C3%ADnh-T%C3%BD-h%E1%BA%A1-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-Vi%E1%BB%87t-H%E1%BA%A3i-%C4%91%C3%ACnh-b%E1%BB%99-%C4%91%C3%ACnh-ch%E1%BB%A7-Tri%E1%BB%87u-Phong-th%C3%A1i-th%C3%BA-H%C3%A0-Thi%E1%BA%BFu-Trai-nguy%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-xf2zkGChSwq59E8djSRgzw">Bính Tý hạ đề Việt Hải đình, bộ đình chủ Triệu Phong thái thú Hà Thiếu Trai nguyên vận - 丙子夏題越海亭步亭主肇豐太守何少齋原韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/D%E1%BB%AF-b%E1%BA%A3n-huy%E1%BB%87n-do%C3%A3n-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-nguy%C3%AAn-do%C3%A3n-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-%E1%BA%A9m-t%E1%BB%A9c-t%E1%BB%8Bch-th%C6%B0-ti%E1%BB%85n/poem-xv21OvTa-f2mWcnA0HQ93g">Dữ bản huyện doãn Nguyễn, nguyên doãn Trần đồng ẩm, tức tịch thư tiễn - 與本縣尹阮，原尹陳同飲，即席書餞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-d%E1%BB%8Bch-n%E1%BB%AF-t%E1%BB%AD/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-Tuy%E1%BB%81n-kh%C3%AA/poem-RIoAkWL75nfKFdR9QG-s8g">Đề Ngọc Tuyền khê - 題玉泉溪</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-d%E1%BB%8Bch-n%E1%BB%AF-t%E1%BB%AD/author-3Hi3GBlQH1Jir1987XfL5Q">Tương dịch nữ tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/Kinh-Tri%E1%BB%87u-do%C3%A3n-h%E1%BB%93i-h%C6%B0u/poem-4NI7HwvDt0r8DC6semHm5w">Kinh Triệu doãn hồi hưu - 京兆尹回休</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Y-S%C6%A1n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/Ng%C3%B4n-ch%C3%AD/poem-L5VycOEV23__0xXY7DWnwQ">Ngôn chí - 言志</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Y-S%C6%A1n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-4hqqwjm5ILG91lb8l2Pqvw">Y Sơn thiền sư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-%C4%90i%E1%BB%83n-Thi%E1%BA%BFt-t%E1%BB%B1-Thi-Ch%C3%A2u-quy/poem-Wtg7pr18QYwpC7wnveu-vw">Trịnh Điển Thiết tự Thi Châu quy - 鄭典設自施州歸</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Huy-T%E1%BA%A5n/Tr%C3%B9ng-qu%C3%A1-H%C6%B0ng-Long-t%E1%BB%B1-l%C6%B0u-bi%E1%BB%87t-Li%C3%AAn-Th%C3%A0nh-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/poem-q05eNSr2s5hnrpf10G9JOw">Trùng quá Hưng Long tự lưu biệt Liên Thành thiền sư - 重過興隆寺留別連城禪師</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Huy-T%E1%BA%A5n/author-Ptt2M8z98OAIiQfyBrIxHw">Vũ Huy Tấn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tuy%E1%BB%87t-c%C3%BA-m%E1%BA%A1n-h%E1%BB%A9ng-k%E1%BB%B3-8/poem-lhlBXuDa4lVE7rh3_Q33Ww">Tuyệt cú mạn hứng kỳ 8 - 絕句漫興其八</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/V%E1%BB%8Dng-H%C3%A1n-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-li%E1%BB%85u-s%E1%BA%AFc-k%C3%BD-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-T%E1%BB%83/poem-40-2nrF_oL0kZSOVgPnaTQ">Vọng Hán Dương liễu sắc ký Vương Tể - 望漢陽柳色寄王宰</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
